overview.en: YT is a value circulation tool developed by the blockchain technology team of Fujian Winxin Industrial Co., Ltd. The team members have many years of experience in R&D, operation and maintenance of blockchain technology, and have their own unique insights into blockchain technology.
overview.zh: YT通证是福建赢新实业有限公司区块链技术团队研发的价值流通工具，团队成员均拥有多年的区块链技术研发、运营维护经验，对区块链技术有自己独特的见解。
